programme.title: Workshop Vagabond Vacations
programme.desc: JONA ​​and JC, our faithful vloggers, continue to surprise us! This time, they organize crazy photoshoots all over the world! Incredible models, dreamscapes, international photographers... With their touch of humor that we all know well, they make us live their adventures as directors, photographers and lovers... In this 1st episode in Costa Rica, Nature is the most beautiful set for our models and photographers. These photoshoots will blow your mind!
